title: What's Behind Carter's Claim That Russia Will Suffer Casualties in Syria?
text: When US Defense Secretary Ash Carter said that he expects Russia will soon suffer casualties, his phrase sparked the question whether the Pentagon has a Soviet-Afghanistan redux in mind for Syria, Germany-based political scientist and analyst Phil Butler remarks. ...
